0:0:55,166 --> 0:1:0,786
and impact whether in
Detroit or in Brazil.


18
0:1:0,786 --> 0:1:3,666
And throughout her leadership,
she's been a strong advocate


19
0:1:3,666 --> 0:1:7,746
of the contributions,
creativity, and the innovation


20
0:1:7,746 --> 0:1:11,516
of Michigan student,
staff, faculty, and alumni.


21
0:1:11,516 --> 0:1:13,956
And most importantly, for
the Board of Regents we are


22
0:1:13,956 --> 0:1:16,196
so excited because Mary
Sue Coleman has brought us


23
0:1:16,196 --> 0:1:22,96
