25
0:1:25,906 --> 0:1:30,706
staff, and students do all
the great work that they do.


26
0:1:30,706 --> 0:1:33,346
So please join me in welcoming
the president of the University


27
0:1:33,346 --> 0:1:35,516
of Michigan, Dr.
Mary Sue Coleman.


28
0:1:35,516 --> 0:1:46,66
